metadata.name: Spiritual Monolith
metadata.description:
There are many temples in Thailand, but this one is very special. Right at the center of the city called Nakhon Pathom. Land this great stupa "Phra Pathommachedi" the tallest stupa in Thailand.
This image has been taken at the city festival time on a very private spot. 
I really love this place at that moment, it really represent the closest imagination I had with the reality.

This shot has been taken with A7S3 with 200-600mm lens.
The image has been enhanced for a higher resolutions.
